sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Istio Ingress Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Activator as Knative Activator<br/>80/TCP HTTP mTLS
    participant Predictor as Predictor Pod<br/>8080/TCP HTTP mTLS
    participant Storage as S3/GCS Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+

    Note over Client,Storage: Flow 1: Model Inference Request (Serverless Mode)

    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/models/model:predict<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (optional)
    Gateway->>Activator: Forward Request<br/>HTTP/80 mTLS (Istio)
    Activator->>Predictor: Inference Request<br/>HTTP/8080 mTLS
    Predictor->>Predictor: Load Model from Local Volume
    Predictor-->>Activator: Prediction Result<br/>HTTP/8080 mTLS
    Activator-->>Gateway: Response<br/>HTTP/80 mTLS
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON Response<br/>HTTPS/443

    Note over Client,Storage: Flow 2: Model Deployment

    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Webhook as KServe Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Controller as KServe Controller<br/>Watch/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant KnativeAPI as Knative Serving API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+

    Client->>K8sAPI: kubectl apply InferenceService<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: Validate/Mutate<br/>HTTPS/443 mTLS
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Admission Response
    K8sAPI->>Controller: CR Update Event (Watch)
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Resources<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>Auth: Service Account
    Controller->>KnativeAPI: Create Knative Service<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>Auth: Service Account
    KnativeAPI-->>Controller: Service Created

    Note over Client,Storage: Flow 3: Model Download

    participant StorageInit as Storage Initializer<br/>Init Container
    participant Volume as Local Volume<br/>emptyDir

    StorageInit->>Storage: Download Model Artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>Auth: AWS IAM/GCP SA
    Storage-->>StorageInit: Model Files
    StorageInit->>Volume: Write to emptyDir
    Predictor->>Volume: Read Model Files<br/>Local Filesystem

    Note over Client,Storage: Flow 4: InferenceGraph Pipeline

    participant Router as InferenceGraph Router<br/>8080/TCP HTTP mTLS
    participant Transformer as Transformer Service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP mTLS

    Client->>Gateway: POST /v2/models/graph:infer<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Gateway->>Router: Forward Request<br/>HTTP/8080 mTLS
    Router->>Transformer: Transform Input<br/>HTTP/8080 mTLS
    Transformer-->>Router: Transformed Data
    Router->>Predictor: Predict<br/>HTTP/8080 mTLS
    Predictor-->>Router: Prediction
    Router-->>Gateway: Final Result<br/>HTTP/8080 mTLS
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON Response<br/>HTTPS/443
